{"tid":2101504,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"黃世澤：美國繼唔繼續加碼 就係睇今次初選點","createTime":"2020-07-10T00:35:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T04:33:13.000Z","uid":24814,"like":45,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"920a9e6e730da72f3e2b06ea0a6382a88d87fb91","tid":2101504,"uid":24814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T00:35:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AKUuD-vuxzc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAKUuD-vuxzc&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjt%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=872ae482\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AKUuD-vuxzc</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https://i.pinimg.com/originals/01/d2/0a/01d20a76f23b0ec294ebea37072084fd.jpg&amp;h=078cfc63&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/35-19_ufzBP_1200x0.png&amp;h=c1246f58&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>日期： 7 月 11 日至 12 日<br />\n時間：上午9時至下午9時<br />\n地點：共251個票站，見下圖，或點擊以下連結</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hd0gHM7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHd0gHM7.png&h=d4f7a916&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3NJJ7dO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3NJJ7dO.png&h=2d51c7e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zsGS0yO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzsGS0yO.png&h=76ac07ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LpYBHM9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLpYBHM9.png&h=ee5f8d7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n7oYV7a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn7oYV7a.png&h=ae4166f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tSq8yTQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtSq8yTQ.png&h=fe88f195&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/民主派初選-251-票站位置資料一覽-周末攜身份證-地址證明可投票/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E5%88%9D%E9%81%B8-251-%E7%A5%A8%E7%AB%99%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%BD-%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%AB%E6%94%9C%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E8%AD%89-%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80%E8%AD%89%E6%98%8E%E5%8F%AF%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%2F&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjt%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=ff56c04e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E5%88%9D%E9%81%B8-251-%E7%A5%A8%E7%AB%99%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%BD-%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%AB%E6%94%9C%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E8%AD%89-%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80%E8%AD%89%E6%98%8E%E5%8F%AF%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%2F&h=a4d23964\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/民主派初選-251-票站位置資料一覽-周末攜身份證-地址證明可投票/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>簡易Q&amp;A</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"teal\"><span class=\"x-large\">Q：初選係民間非正式投票，點解要谷投票率？</span></span><br />\nA：因為初選結果只係「口頭約束」，技術上只能靠參選人自律遵守，但如果有民意把關，不論係當選人，或落選人，都較難推翻選舉結果。<br />\n<br />\n舉例，如最後初選只有500人投票，落選人大可聲稱初選未反映民意，堅決參選，令初選失去意義；而如果有10萬人投票，落選人反口，即使佢堅持參選，亦即係背向10萬民意，參選都好難贏，令初選有實際意義。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"teal\"><span class=\"x-large\">Q：國安法殺到，35+都無撚用啦，仲玩黎做乜？</span></span><br />\n<br />\nA：<br />\n一、香港最高級別全民公開選舉已屬立法會選舉，唔單止係選代議士，亦係對執政者（香港政府，中共）既民意反映，如大家唔投票，亦等於默許過去一年中共港共既行為。同理，是次初選因距離國安法立法日子極近，亦係目前民間極少數完全合法既群體表態活動，一定會被本地、中共、海外視為民意反映。<br />\n<br />\n二、公民社會同極權社會之間既戰爭唔係殲滅戰，而係「拔河戰」（tug of war），唔止係鬥力，亦係鬥邊個先鬆懈同放棄。你唔知對手幾時會鬆懈，但你就係等緊果一刻，任何情況下，有權要拎盡，有選舉要贏盡，未來既野無人知，要做好一切準備。<br />\n<br />\n三、外國已留意到今次初選公投，亦認同佢既民意合法性。如果夠多人其實係一次國際線成績，相反，如果少人投無人理，就代表國安法成功，大家已自動滅聲。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"teal\"><span class=\"x-large\">Q：如果DQ曬所有參加初選既人，咁初選仲有咩意義？</span></span><br />\n<br />\nA：DQ本來就係人治不合理暴政，你無辦法去防止對家做任何DQ行為，對家隨時都可以做，但未做之前，你唔應該以未發生既事去自我審查，正如你唔夠因為有可能炒車就唔坐交通工具。相反，係DQ未發生之前，就可以繼續用「拔河戰」概念去應對，有權要拎盡，有選舉要贏盡。"},{"pid":"b0f5797487517b5bdf624eefab691ff8553f2ca4","tid":2101504,"uid":24814,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T00:36:49.000Z","msg":"2020立法會選舉 民主派初選論壇 - 新界東<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bnGWmSrhpeU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbnGWmSrhpeU&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjt%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=57eeab08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bnGWmSrhpeU</a><br />\n<br />\n2020立法會選舉 民主派初選論壇 - 港島區<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jcoguARO8c4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjcoguARO8c4&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjt%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=e8d77d93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jcoguARO8c4</a><br />\n<br />\n2020立法會選舉 民主派初選論壇 - 九龍東<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pO427K5M9sM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpO427K5M9sM&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjt%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=56a56c47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pO427K5M9sM</a><br />\n<br />\n2020立法會選舉 民主派初選論壇 - 超級區議會<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qCjmKYz2eU4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqCjmKYz2eU4&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjt%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=84e7352b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qCjmKYz2eU4</a><br />\n<br />\n2020立法會選舉 民主派初選論壇 - 九龍西<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J4WtiJG_Eb4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJ4WtiJG_Eb4&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjt%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=4aa7b4f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watc